清楚她与梅根·西·斯塔林 (Megan Thee Stallion) 合作的新歌是否仅仅是一首独立单曲，还是将作为潜在第二张专辑的一部分出现。这位说唱歌手的真名是 Belcalis Marlenis Almánzar，但尚未公布第二张 LP 的任何细节，尽管最近整个夏天都很忙，与说唱界的更多大牌合作。</p><p>其中包括她与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/offset">Offset</a>合作制作的单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/offset-on-jamie-lee-curtis-staring-in-jealousy-video-shes-a-real-one-3480119">“Jealousy”</a> 、与 FendiDa Rappa 合作的“Point Me 2”，以及与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/latto">Latto</a>合作的单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-latto-and-cardi-b-have-fun-in-the-put-it-on-da-floor-again-video-3450658">“Put It On Da Floor Again”</a> 。</p><p>至于 Megan Thee Stallion，这位说唱歌手于去年 8 月发行了她的第二张录音室专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/megan-thee-stallion-traumazine-album-review-future-rico-nasty-3290072-3290072">《Traumazine》</a> ，此后又在 Disney+ 系列剧集<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/she-hulk"><em>《女浩克：律师》</em></a>中客串出演。</p><p>然而最近，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tory-lanez">托里·拉内兹 (Tory Lanez)</a>因枪杀她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tory-lanez-sentenced-to-10-years-in-prison-for-megan-thee-stallion-shooting-3480329">而被判处 10 年监禁</a>后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-addresses-haters-on-stage-following-tory-lanez-sentencing-3483108">这位艺术家猛烈抨击了她的“仇恨者”</a> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3493412" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3493412" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3493412" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Megan-Thee-Stallion-Cardi-B@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Cardi B 和 Megan Thee Stallion 在第 63 届格莱美奖颁奖典礼上表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Megan-Thee-Stallion-Cardi-B@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Megan-Thee-Stallion-Cardi-B@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Megan-Thee-Stallion-Cardi-B@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uplo